    "rationale": "The credibility assessment was reviewed and accepted for submission. All 13 factors were evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were flagged as epistemic gaps. Achieved levels fall below required levels across all assessed factors, consistent with a Not Accepted regulatory decision. The package is accepted as a complete credibility evidence record for submission to the regulatory dossier, notwithstanding the identified gaps. Validation experiments were performed across multiple operating points and results are documented inline; provenance documentation for all experimental activities is noted as partially incomplete.",
